---
title: Bang Bang Tofu Tacos with Crunchy Red Cabbage-Carrot Slaw
description: Be prepared to be bowled over by flavour from this twist on bang bang tacos. Hearty crisped tofu is tossed in sweet chili sauce, nestled in flour tortillas with crunchy slaw and drizzled with spicy mayo to spice up your life!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tacos-de-tofu-bang-bang-78383d2f.jpg
